      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard expectations of the pre-owned market. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from its flawless exterior luster to the showroom-fresh interior\u2014reflects a rigorous standard of climate-controlled preservation and fastidious maintenance. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically unrivaled, this vehicle offers an acquisition opportunity for the most discerning collector who prioritizes uncompromising quality and historical integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
